In triangle $ABC,$ $AB = 9,$ $BC = 10,$ and $AC = 11.$  If $D$ and $E$ are chosen on $\overline{AB}$ and $\overline{AC}$ so that $AD = 4$ and $AE = 7,$ then find the area of triangle $ADE.$

